Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.10,0:00:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.60,0:00:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.60,0:00:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这很完美
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.50,0:00:18.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.40,0:00:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能保证一件事
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.20,0:00:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝对不会
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.20,0:00:35.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让高桥哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:04.80,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}嘘つきなあなた 泣き虫のあたし
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:10.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どうして？ うまくいかないわ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:16.67,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}オシャレした髪も ラインストーンの爪も
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.57,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたは気付きもしないね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:29.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}LOVE 悲しい涙なんかじゃないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:34.70,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}目が乾いてヒリヒリするだけ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:40.96,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}転んでばっかり I LOVE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:49.20,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}君だけを あたしだけを
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:54.18,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}熱い想いを受け止めて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:01.37,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこまでも つながってたい
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:06.20,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛くない泣き顔も
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.22,op_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}全部愛してね
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.90,0:01:04.80,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}谎话连篇的你 爱哭鼻子的我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.85,0:01:10.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}怎么进展得不顺利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.94,0:01:16.67,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}精心打扮的头发 光彩夺目的指甲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.93,0:01:22.57,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你却都没注意到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.87,0:01:29.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}love 并非悲伤的泪水
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.14,0:01:34.70,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}干涩的眼睛只是有些刺痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:40.96,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}泪水滚落不停 I love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.78,0:01:49.20,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只有你 只有我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.73,0:01:54.18,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}理解那炽热的思念
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:02:01.37,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}无论在哪里 都彼此相连
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.88,0:02:06.20,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}连你并不可爱的哭脸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.44,0:02:08.22,op_chs,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我也深爱
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你送我回家
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里 你今天还是暖暖身子早些睡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.40,0:02:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.70,0:03:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才 去车站前没找到你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.60,0:03:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽约的事抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.40,0:03:11.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回去
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.90,0:03:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,进屋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.90,0:03:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到把她弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.00,0:04:01.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得没什么大不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实 你对山本没任何想法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.40,0:04:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才能去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.00,0:04:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为没什么可顾忌的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.80,0:04:19.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 对高桥来说就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.80,0:04:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么才能劝说没自信的高桥接受你的做法
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跟高桥的感受方式根本就不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.90,0:04:37.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想批评你去山本那
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.30,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的不是对与不对
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.10,0:04:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要伤害高桥吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.50,0:06:27.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没想到把她弄哭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.50,0:06:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,觉得没什么大不了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 对高桥就不一样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.40,0:06:49.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你伤害高桥了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.20,0:07:00.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妈的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.50,0:07:38.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么 感冒啦？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.60,0:07:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脸好红啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.60,0:07:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨夜用了两小时走回家
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.90,0:07:46.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？顶着雪？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.80,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车钱不够了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出租车打太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.70,0:07:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歇歇吧 会倒下的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.50,0:07:54.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.30,0:07:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.00,0:08:02.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 七七也终于…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.50,0:08:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们跟你父母一样担心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.20,0:08:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 怎么样 顺利吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.60,0:08:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那个啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.30,0:08:25.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.30,0:08:27.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 我得去取日志
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.60,0:08:28.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.70,0:08:33.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.30,0:08:35.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.00,0:08:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.10,0:09:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.50,0:09:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.00,0:09:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那家伙摔倒了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.40,0:09:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才早退了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.20,0:09:17.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.30,0:09:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发烧厉害吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.80,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.00,0:09:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说只是感冒了 先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.40,0:09:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难道你是躲着我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.50,0:09:39.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有这种事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.20,0:09:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他爽约去找山本同学了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.50,0:09:49.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 真差劲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.60,0:09:51.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七七 那是你任性
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.20,0:09:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.30,0:09:56.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没选自己而是选了别的女人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.50,0:09:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不过分吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.30,0:10:01.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是毫不隐瞒也确实联系过
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.50,0:10:06.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像出这种事的时候没办法啊 太不体谅了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.40,0:10:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 是这样么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.70,0:10:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 为什么必须忍耐的不是山本而是七七呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.20,0:10:15.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是女朋友吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.70,0:10:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总让他把你摆在第一位怎么行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.30,0:10:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖对方的话就不会这么唠叨了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.90,0:10:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖 正因为有这种事才没法信赖吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.10,0:10:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么就不是对方而是自己的问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.70,0:10:32.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己的问题？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.10,0:10:37.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是矢野没想到会这么糟才去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.00,0:10:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还信赖了你 不是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.90,0:10:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.50,0:10:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我的父母病倒了矢野就不会来
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.90,0:10:51.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说 你没给矢野打电话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.60,0:10:54.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呜呜哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.60,0:10:55.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉 好伤心
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.40,0:10:57.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会去的 小水
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.40,0:11:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也会去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.70,0:11:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,信赖吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.30,0:11:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直缺少的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.30,0:11:24.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总觉得 每次都在一个地方碰壁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.70,0:11:27.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我跟山本做过
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.70,0:11:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那件事我没法从心底原谅他吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.50,0:11:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 是我有问题吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.40,0:11:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.00,0:12:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别再让我不安了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.20,0:12:26.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:28.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧已经退了不少
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.00,0:12:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你睡了一整天啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.70,0:12:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个 有人来看望你 让人进来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:38.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.50,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那样躺着就好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.40,0:12:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感觉怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.40,0:12:56.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说要发展成肺炎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:58.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没什么 已经没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.20,0:13:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗 两天没来学校我很担心
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.60,0:13:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笔记 帮你复印了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.70,0:13:12.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了 有别人会借我看笔记
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.00,0:13:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我切蜜瓜了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.10,0:13:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.20,0:13:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家来看望你啊 元晴 说谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.40,0:13:29.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.90,0:13:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿姨 好漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.70,0:13:45.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感冒也许会传上你 吃完赶紧回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.50,0:13:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很少感冒 没关…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是来了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.60,0:14:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其实我还不想见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.80,0:14:15.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两天没来还是挺担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.80,0:14:18.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到就马上回…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.30,0:14:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.20,0:14:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,山本同学
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.10,0:14:42.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说这些话是有些自私
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.50,0:14:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你别再给矢野打电话 也别再见他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.30,0:14:48.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.40,0:14:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为矢野在和我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.80,0:14:53.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就和他本人说
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.90,0:14:59.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为山本同学是奈奈的妹妹
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.20,0:15:03.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般的外人不一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.80,0:15:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以矢野的判断不理智
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.60,0:15:10.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没把他看成姐姐的男朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.90,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道什么 当他女朋友最多才一年
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.70,0:15:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 和姐姐交往前的矢野也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.60,0:15:25.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐死去后的矢野也好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.30,0:15:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哭得死去活来的矢野也好我全知道
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.00,0:15:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的事 我能理解的比你多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.00,0:15:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比你多得多
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.90,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道的事没办法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.20,0:16:01.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是说 不好的是我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.20,0:16:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.90,0:16:06.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的理解不够吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.20,0:16:11.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她说知道最痛苦时的矢野
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:16.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我在努力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.60,0:16:18.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拼命地 拼命地
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:22.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 还差得太远吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.30,0:16:24.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.60,0:16:26.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要勉强
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,努力是对的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 不可能真正理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.20,0:16:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像你希望他这样他做不到一样
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.30,0:16:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望你理解的你也理解不了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.10,0:16:47.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没办法的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.90,0:16:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是思考方式的不同
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.10,0:17:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 怎么才好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.70,0:17:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.80,0:17:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 你一个人？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才听见你声音 跟谁说话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.50,0:17:28.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在 打手机
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看望就算了 会传上你的回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.30,0:17:37.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷的 关上窗户吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.80,0:17:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竹内 我根本不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.10,0:17:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.70,0:17:53.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么交往才不会伤害高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.20,0:17:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人总有缺点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.40,0:18:02.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是现在才开始想的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.60,0:18:09.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种事 是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.50,0:18:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.80,0:18:17.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真够没出息的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.50,0:18:28.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法原谅哭泣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.40,0:18:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}可是 我没有以后不再伤害她的自信
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.30,0:18:44.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}但是 只有高桥她绝对不想放弃
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.80,0:18:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:19:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}怎么了 不睡觉不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.20,0:19:04.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真的没人来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.40,0:19:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,诶 没人来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.20,0:19:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}元晴 不许出去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.30,0:19:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.50,0:19:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.80,0:19:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁也没在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.50,0:19:35.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,元晴 看清楚 谁也没在吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.50,0:19:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,烧退了也不能疏忽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.90,0:19:59.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高桥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.40,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.80,0:20:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我软弱的时候别对我温柔
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.20,0:20:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,软弱的 时候
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.80,0:20:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好狡猾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.80,0:20:36.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 笑笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.50,0:20:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露出平常开心的表情 想你平时一样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.70,0:20:45.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那样我就…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.80,0:20:51.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真没用
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.30,0:20:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是 我为什么哭呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.90,0:21:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的话会一直让你微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟他在一起不幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直在我身边
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.40,0:21:05.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不幸福吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.90,0:21:08.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那为什么还维持那种关系
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.60,0:21:11.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找我之前我会先找到
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.40,0:21:14.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会为你做你想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.00,0:21:17.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能让它们正当化的动机只有一个呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.90,0:21:25.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想不到的话 就说明你没那个资格吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.90,0:21:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我更能让高桥幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.40,0:21:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有件事想和你说
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.10,0:21:41.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然是这个时候… 可你平时又不怎么在家
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.70,0:21:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想离婚
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.70,0:22:00.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我比他更能让高桥幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.00,0:22:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}其实我发了一年愁了 总是不能下定决心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.80,0:22:12.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 一个多月前一位老朋友来电话
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.20,0:22:17.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该知道 就是那位前服装师
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.50,0:22:19.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不能再置之不理了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问我能不能给她帮些忙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.60,0:22:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个年纪能不能找到工作是我最担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.20,0:22:32.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我觉得是个机会 不想错过它
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.20,0:22:39.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(424,470)}哭泣也好 烦恼也好 都让他们结束吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.00,0:22:46.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,两个人在一起 不是该更开心些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.30,0:22:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去东京吗
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.40,0:23:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想保护你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.10,0:23:23.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个夜晚 我祈祷同样的梦而入睡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.80,0:23:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,醒来的早晨 却已不同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.50,0:23:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未来 还看不清
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.40,0:25:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我或许是不适合矢野的女孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.20,0:25:13.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的心情我一点儿也不理解
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.50,0:25:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们为什么做不到那些简单的事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.50,0:25:25.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 我更正两年前的话
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.20,0:25:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之 都注定是最差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:37.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}季節が少し動いた気がする
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:46.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}陽射しも短く　いつかずれて
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:54.70,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}二人のバスは　変わらない街
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:19:02.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}走っていること　ホッとしてた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:11.90,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}窓の外　いつもみたいに見てるあなた
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:23.30,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}そしてわたしも真似をしている いつもみたいに
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:32.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　ふたりは　おなじなのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}行きたい場所は？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.20,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}黙っていたって　いいんだよね？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:49.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ねぇ　ふたりは　同じなのかな？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いとしい気持ち……
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:59.10,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あなたの視線は　いま、見えなくて……
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.80,0:18:37.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我感到季节略微变换
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:46.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}阳光不知在何时变短
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:54.70,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}只要公交车仍在那街道行驶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.10,0:19:02.40,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}两人就把心放宽
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.40,0:19:11.90,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你总是一如既往地望向窗外
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.20,0:19:23.30,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}于是我也学着你 一如既往
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.50,0:19:32.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 我们两个是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.00,0:19:35.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}要去的地方是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.80,0:19:40.20,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}沉默不语 这样好吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.20,0:19:49.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}喂 我们两个是一样的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.80,0:19:52.50,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}爱恋的感觉是一样吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.70,0:19:59.10,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你的视线 如今我看不见…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:52.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}しずかな雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:59.84,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すこしつめたい雨
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:07.45,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}あたたまり続けてる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:14.87,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この心を冷やすように
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:22.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつもキミをみつけていた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:26.86,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}優しい後ろすがた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:31.05,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まわりゆくこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.78,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこへむかうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.89,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}キミがみつめる先には
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:47.98,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにがあるだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:55.95,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等はひたはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:03.12,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とどきそうで　とどかない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:05.16,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.53,0:23:16.44,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}しずかに雨が降る
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.20,0:23:23.47,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}すこしさびしい雨
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.00,0:23:31.02,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}ひろがり続けてる
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.47,0:23:38.36,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}この心を宥めるように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.95,0:23:46.32,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}いつもキミを　みつめている
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.42,0:23:50.35,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}可愛い後ろすがた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.40,0:23:54.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}まわりゆくこの想い
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:58.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}どこにむかうの？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.63,0:24:04.54,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕がもとめる先には
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.84,0:24:11.67,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}なにが待つだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.24,0:24:19.74,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等はひたはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.76,0:24:26.74,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}おいつけそうで　おいつかない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.87,0:24:28.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.38,0:24:48.50,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}僕等はひたはしる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.59,0:24:55.62,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}とどきそうで　とどかない
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.79,0:24:57.40,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.56,0:25:01.34,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:05.17,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.84,0:25:08.73,ED_JP,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}その距離で
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.90,0:21:52.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}平静的雨滴落下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.40,0:21:59.84,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}它有些冰冷
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.18,0:22:07.45,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}就像要冰冻这颗
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.82,0:22:14.87,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}不断温暖的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.28,0:22:22.67,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我总是找到了你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.73,0:22:26.86,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}找到你温柔的背影
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.75,0:22:31.05,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}旋转的这份思念
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.22,0:22:34.78,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}将去向何方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.22,0:22:40.89,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}你注视的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.23,0:22:47.98,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}有些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.65,0:22:55.95,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}我们奔驰不息
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.02,0:23:03.12,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}若即若离
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.21,0:23:05.16,ED_CN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)}那微妙的距离
